column5: Guyz i got a open spot for Quinte for friday may 13th till monday the 16th, $75 covers you for 3 nites 4 days, plus we split the gas and you bring a meal for  4 guyz, you"ll be fishing out of my bassboat with me,Come on guyz i need someone sucks fishing by myself!
Wish I could bud! Ill be down on lake chatauqua next weekend chasing bass finally!! Enjoy the trip bud, lookin forward to hittin the water with ya again this season.
Can't do it Wayne.  I would strongly recommend this.  Wayne is quality all the way. We all had a blast last year with 2 fishing in Wayne's boat and the other 2 in mine.
Sorry fella or I'd go back.. sitting in Sinai all week.

Going to miss ya this year DAve, Wayne take care of business buddy!First meal of the trip is a steak dinner cooked by myself, although Dave did complain they were alittle small!!!Maybe next time Darrel, see ya on erie!
I forgot to mention all other meals are covered!
Glad to hear it Wayne.  I hope you pound the walleye.
